	 Prof. Peter Barker, [in:] "Journal for the History of Astronomy" vol. 36, Nov. 2005, part 4,  p. 454; 
	 Prof. Kristian Peder Moesgaard [in:] "Centaurus" 2006, vol. 48, p. 114; 
	 Prof. Wilburn Applebaum, [in:] "Isis", vol. 97 (2006), p. 153-154 (this review contains some 
	errors which I explain [in:] "Letter to the Editor", [in:] ISIS, vol. 98, September 2007, p. 608-609); 
	 Prof. James Evans, in: "Early Science and Medicine", vol. 11 (2006) fascymile 3 (August 2006), 
	 p. 357-59. 

	 
	 
	

